{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; DISPONE FRECUENCIA QUE INDICA</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; N&#xFA;m. 191 exenta.- Antofagasta, 18 de Julio de 1995.- Visto: el art&#xED;culo 12, del D.S. 212/92, del Ministerio de Transportes y Telecomunicaciones, Subsecretar&#xED;a de Transportes</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Resuelvo:</div><br><br><br><br></div>", "i": 6021253}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1) Disp&#xF3;nese la siguiente frecuencia m&#xED;nima por hora y sentido de tr&#xE1;nsito, para los servicios de locomoci&#xF3;n colectiva urbana en las comunas de Antofagasta y Calama.</div><div class=\"p\"> Comunas&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Horario&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Frecuencia</div><div class=\"p\"> Antofagasta&nbsp;  07.00 a 09.00 hrs.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  10 (diez)</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; veh&#xED;culos por</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; hora y sentido</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; de tr&#xE1;nsito.</div><div class=\"p\"> Calama&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 07.00 a 09.00 hrs.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  8 (ocho)</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; veh&#xED;culos por</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; hora y sentido</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbs